{"tid":1586560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警察內心世界","createTime":"2019-09-22T04:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T04:27:22.000Z","uid":263448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"52c47e7edec39a1b2e03fecdef46fddd25de96ab","tid":1586560,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:19:46.000Z","msg":"警察內心世界：<br />\n1.醫生、救護、記者、街坊、機師、老師、學生、社工、議員、小朋友...都係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">曱甴扮既</span></span>。<br />\n2.打錯人、拉錯人、殺錯人，都係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">曱甴累既</span></span>。<br />\n3.強姦曱甴係因為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">曱甴累既</span></span>。<br />\n4.有街坊聲澳俱下咁罵我地係假既，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">演員黎既</span></span>。<br />\n5.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記者都係黑既</span></span>，除咗HKG、TVB、東方、大公文匯，其他都係黑既。<br />\n6.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">啲救護係曱甴扮既</span></strong>，佢地話救我地？點知會唔會搞死我地？<br />\n7.<strong>黑社會合作，係社會和諧、係深明大義；曱甴搞事係破壞社會和諧</strong>。<br />\n8.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我賺錢多過曱甴，我好叻，所以我無比人洗腦；曱甴賺錢少，係佢地蠢，佢地比人洗腦</span></strong>。<br />\n9.我地係最大最威，連<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中共都認可我地</strong></span>，其他乜乜柒柒部門，都食屎啦。<br />\n10.<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>指揮果班人都係無腦<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">食屎大</span></strong></span>，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">開真槍殺晒佢地</span></strong>，<span style=\"color: red;\">有殺錯無放過</span>，企得係現場都係曱甴，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>殺錯良民係佢地抵死</strong></span>，洗理外國勢力講乜？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dz6Vdt1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDz6Vdt1.jpg&h=da3b3723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n輸咗既話，未來連2歳細路比警察拉都入到罪。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQG6j9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQG6j9e.jpg&h=fb51b98a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾時連藍絲都係扮既，我地勝選又多咗，好似係。"},{"pid":"013b8342ae49cf816c0a32c7457f850ea8a57b12","tid":1586560,"uid":253479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc56c78f759578046748666c8d7a90ae0ada6ec2","tid":1586560,"uid":15323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:27:22.000Z","msg":"認同"}]}